trans-unit.source: Defines the base class for resources that can be added to an <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Define a classe base para os recursos que podem ser adicionados a um <xref href="System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Commits all changes and flushes the resource to the document package.
trans-unit.target: Confirma todas as alterações e libera os recursos para o pacote do documento.

trans-unit.source: Based on settings of <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsSerializationManager> and <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsPackagingPolicy>, such as <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.FontSubsetterCommitPolicies> and <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.PackageInterleavingOrder>, the flush operation of the Commit method may be delayed until the whole <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument> is closed.
trans-unit.target: Com base nas configurações de <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsSerializationManager>e <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsPackagingPolicy>, como <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.FontSubsetterCommitPolicies>e <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.PackageInterleavingOrder>, a operação de liberação do método de confirmação pode ser atrasada até que todo o <xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument>está fechado.</xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.XpsDocument> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.Packaging.PackageInterleavingOrder> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.FontSubsetterCommitPolicies> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsPackagingPolicy> </xref:System.Windows.Xps.Serialization.XpsSerializationManager>

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, returns the I/O stream for reading or writing the resource.
trans-unit.target: Quando substituído em uma classe derivada, retorna o fluxo de e/s para ler ou gravar o recurso.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.IO.Stream> for reading or writing the resource.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.IO.Stream>para ler ou gravar o recurso.</xref:System.IO.Stream>

trans-unit.source: Returns the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] of the resource that is relative to a specified absolute [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Retorna o [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] do recurso que é relativo a um absoluto especificado [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The of the resource that is relative to the specified absolute inUri.
trans-unit.target: O do recurso que é relativo ao absoluto especificado inUri .
